metadata.name: Mimozis
metadata.description:
Our bodies, like blossoming flowers, possess a fleeting beauty that flourishes for but a brief interlude. Like unfurling petals, our unique forms and expressions captivate the world around us. As I reflect on this transience, I am reminded to embrace the fleeting beauty of my own physical existence, cherishing every moment as it delicately unfolds, knowing that its ephemeral nature makes it all the more precious

self-portrait  
Tanger, 2023
